OL,3,COnline Safety Act 'missing vital
OL,4,Copportunity' on suicide content
OL,6,FDangerous suicide and self-harm
OL,7,Fcontent will remain online despite the
OL,8,Fintroduction of the Online Safety Act
OL,9,Fbecause of "big gaps around high risk
OL,10,Fcontent", Samaritans has said.
OL,12,FThe charity's policy and influencing
OL,13,Flead said online safety regulator
OL,14,FOfcom is currently choosing to
OL,15,F"ignore" advice from safety groups
OL,16,Faround how it decides which websites
OL,17,Fare in scope of the new rules.
