OL,3,COnline Safety Act 'missing vital
OL,4,Copportunity' on suicide content
OL,6,FJacqui Morrissey told the PA news
OL,7,Fagency that Ofcom has advised the
OL,8,FGovernment to use site user numbers as
OL,9,Fthe criteria for subjecting platforms
OL,10,Fto the strictest measures of the Act `
OL,11,Fwhich would require them to hide or
OL,12,Fremove such content even for users
OL,13,Faged over 18 ` but said that this
OL,14,Fapproach would leave a number of
OL,15,F"small, but very high risk platforms"
OL,16,Fnot subjected to these toughest rules.
OL,18,FThe charity has raised its concerns to
OL,19,Fcoincide with Safer Internet Day
OL,20,F(February 11).
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@eO]
