OL,6,F"The Online Safety Act includes really
OL,7,Fimportant provisions within it that
OL,8,Fenables government to subject small
OL,9,Fbut very high risk platforms to the
OL,10,Fstrictest measures," Ms Morrissey told
OL,11,FPA.
OL,13,F"We are extremely disappointed that
OL,14,FOfcom have chosen to ignore our advice
OL,15,Fand the advice of many organisations
OL,16,Fin making the criteria for the
OL,17,Fstrictest measures focused on the
OL,18,Fnumber of users.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@TO]uD@AOU
