OL,6,FMs Morrissey highlighted studies which
OL,7,Fhad found internet-related use in
OL,8,Fsuicide in 26% of deaths in those
OL,9,Funder 20 and 13% of deaths in 20-to-24-
OL,10,Fyear-olds, and warned that the
OL,11,FGovernment and Ofcom were "missing
OL,12,Fthis vital opportunity".
OL,14,F"These are all people who are over the
OL,15,Fage of 18 who are going to continue to
OL,16,Fcome into contact with this very
OL,17,Fdangerous, very harmful content, which
OL,18,Fisn't going to be covered by the Act
OL,19,Fat the moment," she said.
OL,26,@sD@[OUtD@WO]vD@AOU{D@OO]
