OL,4,Copportunity' on suicide content
OL,6,F"We've heard all too often the role
OL,7,Fthat online forums can play in someone
OL,8,Ftaking their own life. We know
OL,9,Fcoroners have clearly linked deaths to
OL,10,Fa particular site.
OL,12,F"So how much more evidence is needed
OL,13,Fto recognise this level of harm being
OL,14,Fcaused on a site, and to ensure that
OL,15,Fit is subject to the strongest
OL,16,Fmeasures within the Act?
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
