OL,4,Copportunity' on suicide content
OL,6,F"We're saying it is crucial that
OL,7,FGovernment and Ofcom fully harness the
OL,8,Fpower of the Online Safety Act to
OL,9,Fensure people are protected from this
OL,10,Fdangerous content and to make sure
OL,11,Fthat implementation is going to be
OL,12,Feffective as soon as possible."
OL,14,FMs Morrissey added that Samaritans
OL,15,Fbelieves that the level of risk ` for
OL,16,Fexample, if either Ofcom or a coroner
OL,17,F"reasonably link one or more deaths"
OL,18,Fto a particular site ` could be a
OL,19,Fsuitable approach for deciding whether
OL,20,Fa platform should be placed in the
OL,21,Fhighest category of the rules.
