OL,3,COnline Safety Act 'missing vital
OL,4,Copportunity' on suicide content
OL,6,FAn Ofcom spokesperson said: "From next
OL,7,Fmonth, all platforms in scope of the
OL,8,FOnline Safety Act ` including small
OL,9,Fbut risky services ` will have to
OL,10,Fstart taking action to protect people
OL,11,Fof all ages from illegal content,
OL,12,Fincluding illegal suicide and self-
OL,13,Fharm material.
OL,15,F"We won't hesitate to use our robust
OL,16,Fenforcement powers against sites that
OL,17,Fdon't comply with these duties ` which
OL,18,Fcould include applying to a court to
OL,19,Fblock them in the UK in serious cases.
OL,26,@nD@]OUwD@AOU
