OL,6,F"Additional duties such as
OL,7,Fconsistently applying terms of service
OL,8,Fwill be a powerful tool in making
OL,9,Flarger platforms safer in due course.
OL,11,F"But they would do little to tackle
OL,12,Fthe harm done by smaller, riskier
OL,13,Fsites ` as many of them permit harmful
OL,14,Fcontent that is legal."
OL,16,FA Government spokesperson said:
OL,17,F"Suicide devastates families and
OL,18,Fsocial media companies have a clear
OL,19,Fresponsibility to keep people safe on
OL,20,Ftheir platforms.
