OL,6,F"We are determined to keep people safe
OL,7,Fonline by swiftly implementing the
OL,8,FOnline Safety Act which will tightly
OL,9,Fregulate smaller platforms that spread
OL,10,Fhate and suicide content.
OL,12,F"Platforms will need to proactively
OL,13,Fremove illegal suicide material and,
OL,14,Fif accessed by children, protect them
OL,15,Ffrom harmful material ` regardless of
OL,16,Fwhether or not they are a categorised
OL,17,Fservice.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
