OL,6,F"We expect Ofcom to use the full range
OL,7,Fof its powers ` including fining and
OL,8,Fseeking court approval to block access
OL,9,Fto sites ` if these platforms fail to
OL,10,Fcomply."
OL,12,FMs Morrissey added that the charity
OL,13,Fwas also "concerned" by the recent
OL,14,F"rolling back" of certain moderation
OL,15,Fand fact-checking tools by some
OL,16,Fplatforms, most notably Meta, which
OL,17,Flast month said it would replace third-
OL,18,Fparty fact checkers in the US with
OL,19,Fuser-generated community notes and
OL,20,Fwould also loosen content moderation
OL,21,Fon some topics.
