OL,6,F"We would hope that what the Online
OL,7,FSafety Act does is create a minimum
OL,8,Fstandard, but we would hope that
OL,9,Fplatforms go beyond this and implement
OL,10,Fbest practice," she said.
OL,12,F"We know the Act isn't going to cover
OL,13,Flots of kinds of over-18s, dangerous
OL,14,Fcontent, but platforms can choose to
OL,15,Fdo that ` they can choose to make
OL,16,Ftheir platforms as safe as possible
OL,17,Ffor their users.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@OO]tD@AOU
