OL,6,F"So we are concerned that we're
OL,7,Fperhaps seeing some rolling back of
OL,8,Fprogress with platforms recently
OL,9,Faround keeping people safe online.
OL,10,FThat puts us in, I think, a more
OL,11,Fprecarious situation than we were a
OL,12,Fyear ago.
OL,14,F"The internet can be such a positive
OL,15,Fplace. It can be a really important
OL,16,Fspace for people who are feeling
OL,17,Fsuicidal to access really helpful
OL,18,Finformation, to be able to talk to
OL,19,Fpeople who might be experiencing
OL,20,Fsimilar things in a safe and
OL,21,Fsupportive environment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
